Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:10.73,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}a yoke to weigh down those who living with burdens
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:17.52,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}equally, ties everyone down to the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.74,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}a struggle to call down a curse on his fate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:30.29,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}like the dead mob rising to its feet on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.30,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}break today down I'd been living for,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:36.54,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}it'll be the same old yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.83,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}the uncertainty of tomorrow, got shattered
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:46.15,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}even if you look down and shut your heart to it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:51.80,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}the fangs, starving for blood never be gone away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:58.86,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}in this world, it's about to fall into ruin
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:02.15,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}dead that's in vain, wriggles and crawls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.84,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}around everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.85,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}gonna keep on fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.85,0:22:09.91,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}I don't know what it is for
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:13.57,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}having a fear, trembling and tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.86,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur1\fsp-1}I just keep myself together
