Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统命令已经最终确认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰将实施对November Kilo及Romeo Charlie的攻击
