Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的天使们 还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 宽恕我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.15,0:20:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 拯救我们
