Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在的情况
